::KitKat:: 

She turned away from Stringtra and Quickstrike.
She turned and looked at Wildfire. "Be aware. I know your tricks 
horse. I will not fall for them again." she said as she curled her 
upper lip back to show her teeth.  She growled at Wildfire.
"My thoughts are mine and mine alone. I will not allow you to mess 
with my mind. GOT IT!"
She turned and walked out of the base.

She looked back to see the base entrance and then took off into the 
woods.
"Stupid horse. Mind bending horse's tail. I'll not let her mess with 
me any longer."

She stopped running and just loped along letting her anger settle 
down.
